data.description: Welcome home to this updated cozy well-kept 3 bedroom 2.5 bathrooms, corner lot with a roomy backyard located in the lovely Springs of Ellington community. This home is loaded with modern upgraded bathroom vanities, LVP flooring, and backsplash in the kitchen. Half bath on the main level, a versatile sitting/family room offers flexible space, a formal living room with a cozy fireplace, eating dining area overlooking the open kitchen with a walk-in pantry.  Upstairs offers primary owner suit with owner bathroom and a walk-in closet. There are 2 secondary bedrooms with bathrooms a walk-in closet and a roomy laundry. This home is perfectly designed for modern living, an inviting blend of functionality and sophistication.
